Description:
Approximately 11,000m2+ of Prime Development
Set in the heart of Cranbourne East, this is your golden opportunity to purchase over 11,000m2 (Approx) located in the Urban Growth Zone in the Collison Estate. This large block has the potential to sub-divide (STCA) and with new residential development?s taking place around this property now is the time to secure this gold mine.
Not just suitable for the astute developer or investor, the home is also ideal for small or growing families who like ample space and the outdoor lifestyle. The 5 bedroom house offers large living areas with fireplace, outdoor entertainment area, paddocks to house livestock and much more.
Just minutes from schools and shops such as Shopping on Clyde, 76 hectares site full of sporting facilities, park lands, cycling and playgrounds for the kids to play.
Look no further, Contact Corey (Khoi) Le for further information.

Description:
Upgraded Metricon Home Next to Casey Fields
Ideally situated a stones throw from Casey Fields complex and Cranbourne Aquatic Centre is this modern three bedroom home plus study ready to move in. Perfect for any growing family or first home buyer.
Why build when you can buy this one year old home with upgraded appliances and save yourself all the hard work? This home features a spacious master bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite, formal lounge upon entry and an open plan living state of the art kitchen, meals area and lounge. The Kitchen is complete with 5 burner stove, electric oven, dishwasher, stone bench tops and island bench perfect for a Sunday brunch bar. This vast family living area opens out to the outdoor entertaining alfresco area.
Luxury extras including floating timber floors, gas ducted heating, remote control garage with internal access plus much more!
Don't miss this great opportunity to buy in the stunning Mayfield Estate.

Description:
Porter Davis, approx 31 squares, 612sqm block
This amazing 5 year old PORTER DAVIS property redefines the term (LUXURY LIVING). With quality rarely found, this home offers a versatile floor plan with abundant living space & and a variety of inclusions.
The property consists of 4 large bedrooms plus study, master with full enuite with double vanities, oversized shower & 2 WIRs. But that is only the beginning.
The living quarters offer 3 large separate living areas including a closed off formal lounge for the guests, large family living & dining area, in addition to a Rumpus/theatre room. All the living space is centered by an amazing porter Davis kitchen with glass splash back, huge walk in pantry, an abundance of bench space, stone benches, 900mm oven, dishwasher & more.
But that's not all, you also have BI-fold doors that lead onto a big alfresco area that leads to a huge backyard with more than enough space for your kids to play in.
Extra features in the home, include, high ceilings, down lights,

- 4 large bedrooms + study.
- 3 separate living areas including, lounge, family & dining, and rumpus room.
- Huge outdoor alfresco area with bi-fold doors.
- Kitchen with Stainless Steel appliances, glass splash back, stone benches & huge walk in pantry.

This fantastic family home is located in the HUNT CLUB Estate within walking distance to the Cranbourne east primary and secondary schools, parks, & the hunt club village shopping Centre. This property has it all. DO NOT MISS OUT.

Description:
**SOLD BY BRANDON WHITTA**
CRANBOURNE EAST, CASCADES ON CLYDE (124108914): Set in a well-established pocket of Cascades on Clyde this home is absolutely perfect for a family seeking their first home or an upgrade from a smaller unit or house. Given the high demand for rental properties together with the low vacancy rates this is a sensational addition to one's portfolio!
Young, fresh and requiring nothing from you other than to move in, unpack and relax 86 Thunderbolt Drive is easily maintained with features including a generous, open and tiled living/dining area plus a stylish kitchen with stone bench tops, glass splashback and stainless appliances including a 900mm freestanding oven/stove. Don't forget the bonus second living zone which lends itself to a multitude of uses!
There are 4 robed bedrooms to cater for everyone in the family, including the master with a walk-in wardrobe and an ensuite which compliments the family bathroom and second toilet. With ducted heating and evaporative cooling your comfort is ensured all year round!
Step outside to find a remote double garage with internal access and a surprisingly spacious rear yard stretching the full length of the right hand side boundary complete with a covered alfresco for entertaining.
This is a tremendous opportunity for those who insist on nothing but the best! Surrounded by top end properties the location is very appealing and is within close proximity to picturesque wetlands. Other estate features include Class-A recycled water, ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of public open space, BBQ facilities and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Selandra Rise shopping centre which is only a 2 minute (app.) drive away!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*

Description:
3 living areas in the heart of The Hunt Club
In one of the most Sought After Estates in the whole South East this beautiful home located in The Hunt Club has got plenty to offer for any type of buyer. Boasting 3 generous sized bedrooms + a 4th bedroom/study depending on preference of use, the Master with a Walk-in Robe & Ensuite. The entrance opens up to two spacious living areas. There is also the ability to zone off and separate as the front living areas have sliding doors to separate from the 3RD living area at the rear of the home. It also has ducted heating throughout and split system cooling along with 9 foot ceilings. Outside there is a fantastic large area for entertaining and relaxing whilst still having some yard to kick a ball and play. This home also has rear roller door access just to add to the not so common necessities. Another bonus feature is 18 Solar Panels on the roof. To book an inspection CALL JAMES NOW on 0477 799 015!

Description:
HOMES LIKE THESE SPEAK FOR THEMSELVES!
Located in a tightly held pocket within the Cascades on Clyde Estate sits this immaculate four bedroom family home, with an amazing eye for detail this home was designed with the intention to stand out and is sure to satisfy even the most pickiest of buyers!
The master bedroom comes complete with walk in robes and a full ensuite with the addition of a ceiling fan, the remaining generous sized three guest bedrooms are also fitted with built in robes of their own.
Walk through and be taken back by the finishes of the well appointed kitchen area, truly a chefs delight with caesar stone bench tops, glass splash back, 900mm range hood, 5 burner gas cook top, walk in pantry, stainless steel appliances not to mention the ample amounts of bench and overhead storage space. All this overlooking your formal dining/front living area and main living zone.
Added features include: ducted heating, refrigerated cooling, feature lights, down lights, neutral tones throughout, oversized shower space, 8 solar panels, internal access, exposed aggregate driveway and the timber decking walk way alongside a completely landscaped front yard.
Situated on a massive 560m2 block, step outside and enjoy the convenient blend of backyard and alfresco space, providing plenty of room for both adults and children to enjoy.
Surrounded by picturesque wetlands and walk ways, estate features also include Class-A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities and playgrounds. Those who are business savvy will also appreciate the estates Telstra Velocity smart wiring.
Minutes away from Freeway access en route to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre, not to mention walking distance from the Selandra rise shopping centre and hunt club village!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*

CRANBOURNE EAST - HUNT CLUB ESTATE (123917982): **SECOND LIVING ZONE/OPEN STUDY PLUS POWDER ROOM** Set deep in the flourishing Hunt Club Estate, this home perfectly blends space with a low maintenance nature and is positioned in a handy location close to all local amenities. Only a few years young and constructed by popular builders Simonds Homes this would make an ideal first home for a young family and, given that the area is experiencing huge growth, should be in high demand by investors.
Behind its stylish and modern facade you will find a light filled home with living options including a formal lounge and a generous open plan family/meals area which incorporates the stone topped kitchen. Complete with a walk in pantry and stainless appliances, including a 900mm freestanding oven/stove and dishwasher, any cooking enthusiast is bound to be impressed!
There are 3 robed bedrooms, including the master at the rear of the home with both built in and walk in wardrobe facilities and a stylish ensuite to match the equally as impressive family bathroom and separate powder room. Not to forget the ducted heating and evaporative cooling providing year round comfort!
Step outside to find a double remote garage with internal access and a North-facing backyard offering an under-roofline alfresco and covered entertaining deck plus easy to maintain gardens!
Within close proximity to picturesque wetlands and walking/bike paths the Hunt Club is a multi-award winning estate offering a complete range of education facilities including a childcare centre, Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College. Buses weave through the estate whilst the recently opened Hunt Club Village has an array of shopping options. There are future plans for a Cranbourne East railway station as well. High speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs add to the overall appeal of this family orientated location!
The position is second to none! Centrally located to freeways and public transport enroute to the Melbourne CBD which is only app. 40 minutes away. For those of you who like to stay closer to home it?s only a brisk drive to Cranbourne Centro, Berwick Village, Fountain Gate Shopping Centre, Casey Lifestyle Centre and Casey Fields Sporting Complex. Within close vicinity to an array of further Primary, Secondary and Tertiary Institutions the entire family has easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*!

Our floor plans are for representational purposes only and should be used as such. We accept no liability for the accuracy or details contained in our floor plans.

Description:
ENTRY LEVEL BUYING WITH A TRIPLE CAR GARAGE!
If you are looking for a home that provides exceptional value with literally nothing to do but unpack and relax then you have come to the right address!
Perfectly suited to growing families in a location that is second to none - literally seconds to the local bus stop providing easy transport to the recently revamped Cranbourne Centro Shopping centre and brand new Hunt Club Village Shopping centre which is situated directly opposite to the estate. This home boasts convenience!
The master bedroom comes complete with a full ensuite and walk in robe, while your three other generous sized bedrooms are all fixed with built in robes of their own.
Your kitchen, which overlooks the main living area and separate meals zone is fitted out with stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, 4 burner gas cook top and 600mm range hood, plenty of overhead storage with an abundance of bench space.
Added features include: ducted heating, split system cooling, internal access, neutral tones throughout, rear roller door, low maintenance rear and front yard and a massive triple gar garage space!
Surrounded by established homes the property itself is only moments from all of the amenities on offer in the Hunt Club together with childcare and medical facilities, local primary and high school, shops and Chisholm Tafe! Not to forget the recently opened shopping development on Linsell Boulevard, a short 5 minute walk away, offering Safeway, Aldi, takeaway and shopping outlets!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*!

Description:
Brand New, Potential Stamp Duty Savings!
## Mayfield Estate ## Built to Perfection. This home has everything you need. Whether you're a first home buyer, astute investor or downsizing, do not miss this perfect opportunity to own a prime piece of real estate in one of Australia's fastest growing suburbs, Cranbourne East!
Situated on a 448m2 block this home that is currently in its final stages of construction, offering a master bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite, 3 spacious bedrooms with built in robes, laundry, bathroom, separate toilet, open plan kitchen, living and dining. A separate living zone at the back with access to the rear and a double car garage. The kitchen itself is equipped with quality stainless steel products, including a 900mm built in oven and separate cook top, Caesar stone bench tops and plenty of cupboard space to cater for all your master chef needs!
Designed with luxury in mind, other features include;
* Down lights throughout
* Ducted heating
* Split system
* Carpets in bedrooms
* Blinds
* Quality fixtures and fittings
* Landscaping to the front and rear yard
* Potential to save on stamp duty!!
A covered alfresco area caters to your outdoor entertainment needs with plenty of space at the back for the kids to run around and play.
Enquire now and secure your dream home today!

Description:
MAKE YOUR FAMILY HAPPY!!
This is an ideal family home set in a quiet court location. The home consists of three bedrooms with a master with walk in robe and full ensuite. There is also a formal lounge room plus a family room adjoining the kitchen. The rear yard is secure for kids to play even when it rains under the paved and covered outdoor entertainment area.
The home also features a double lock-up garage with a rear roller door and direct internal access to the house.
All this and more plus a water tank, this is a great opportunity.

Description:
Style & Elegance In The Heart Of Casey
A residence like no other, this impressively spacious home caters for the largest of families and is situated in one of the best estates in Cranbourne East.
Flawlessly appointed from top to bottom you will appreciate the grand entry foyer, elegant formal lounge that leads with ease to an amazing kitchen that features stone benchtops, glass splashback, quality Blanco stainless appliances & a huge amount of storage.
The adjoining casual family & meals area offer a relaxed space plus it features a separate rumpus room, home theater to the rear of the home. Cleverly designed with 6 generously proportioned bedrooms (2 with ensuites), 3 bathrooms it offers accommodation that's rarely found.
Extras include: ducted heating, ducted cooling & ducted vacuum, alarm system, spa bath and list goes on.
Outdoors features include beautifully landscaped rear courtyard and an under-cover entertaining area that provides a fine balance to the spacious interiors.
For those looking to make a statement this is the one. Homes of this quality rarely come to the marketplace. Act quickly to avoid disappointment.
